    "HCRs are by and large talented and there are many reasons for a university to attract them beyond the pursuit of higher ranking\" (p. 1022).",
    "The use of HCRs lists in recruitments can be questioned, if different plausible methods exist, and the methods come to different results.",
    "We have demonstrated in this study that HCRs can be differently identified: there is no standard definition of HCRs.",
    "Depending on the methods used and the perspectives taken, very different HCRs lists can be expected-as the empirical results of our study demonstrate.",
